<p><strong>Skills</strong> Perception +3</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1/4 (50 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Pack Tactics.</em></strong> The velociraptor has advantage on an attack roll against a creature if at least one of the velociraptor’s allies is within 5 feet of the creature and the ally isn’t incapacitated.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Multiattack.</em></strong> The velociraptor makes two attacks: one with its bite and one with its claws.</p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. Hit: 5 (1d6+2) piercing damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Claws.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 4 (1d4+2) slashing damage.</p>

